# Get Valeur – eBay Luxury Bag Extension

Browser extension that shows resale intelligence directly on eBay listings
for luxury handbags (Chanel, Hermès, Louis Vuitton…).

## Current status

- Demo overlay working in Chrome on eBay listing pages
- Uses page price to generate fake comparable sales & estimated resale
- Styling aligned with getvaleur.com

## Next steps

- Integrate with eBay APIs once developer account is approved
- Replace fake comps with real historical sales
- Add support for more categories and platforms
